# Plugin runtime artifacts (per-loop, never committed).
# Anchored paths so they don't hide similarly-named files inside the plugin
# code (like commands/plan.md). The ** pattern catches runtime state created
# by tests that cd into nested directories.
/.claude/claudex/
**/.claude/claudex/
/PLAN.md
/reviews/

# Editor/OS noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# Test scratch
/tmp/
